<block wx:if="{{show}}"><view class="privacy-mask data-v-32fbbcc4"><view class="privacy-box y data-v-32fbbcc4"><view class="privacy-title data-v-32fbbcc4">隐私授权</view><view class="privacy-desc data-v-32fbbcc4"> 在使用录音功能之前，请阅读并同意 <text data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['openPrivacyContract',['$event']]]]]}}" class="privacy-link data-v-32fbbcc4" bindtap="__e">{{privacyContractName}}</text> 以继续使用。 </view><view class="privacy-btns x data-v-32fbbcc4"><button data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['handleReject',['$event']]]]]}}" class="p-btn p-reject data-v-32fbbcc4" bindtap="__e">拒绝</button><button class="p-btn p-agree data-v-32fbbcc4" id="agree-btn" open-type="agreePrivacyAuthorization" data-event-opts="{{[['agreeprivacyauthorization',[['handleAgree',['$event']]]]]}}" bindagreeprivacyauthorization="__e">同意</button></view></view></view></block>